ssh dan3stw@hamilton.dur.ac.uk

module load r/gcc/3.6.0
cd /ddn/data/dan3stw
R --save < scratch.R


To Run batch job eg hpc.05.R to hpc.07.R:
for  n  in  `seq  -f  %02g 5 7`
do
echo $n
sbatch   -p  seq7.q    -n  1  --mem-per-cpu=4G job_hpc_v1.slurm   hpc${n}.R 
done

If need to format slurm
dos2unix job_hpc_v1.slurm

To check job status 
sacct   -u  dan3stw
squeue  -u  dan3stw

To cancel a job 
scancel jobid

To cancel all jobs 
scancel  -u  your_user_id

To cancel all pending jobs 
scancel  -t  PD







